OL,3,CCouncil tax up and energy bills down:
OL,4,CHousehold bill changes coming in April
OL,6,FThe price cap sets a limit on the
OL,7,Fmaximum amount suppliers can charge
OL,8,Ffor each unit of gas and electricity
OL,9,Fyou use, and sets a maximum daily
OL,10,Fstanding charge.
OL,12,FThere's no upper threshold for what
OL,13,Fyou actually pay ` if you use more
OL,14,Fenergy, you'll pay more, use less and
OL,15,Fyou'll pay less.
