OL,3,CCouncil tax up and energy bills down:
OL,4,CHousehold bill changes coming in April
OL,6,FSpikes in energy costs, high inflation
OL,7,Fand increases to the National Living
OL,8,FWage have pushed up the cost of
OL,9,Fdelivering services, according to the
OL,10,FLocal Government Association.JThe
OL,11,FGovernment made an extra #600m
OL,12,Favailable to councils for the 2024/25
OL,13,Ftax year, but the County Councils
OL,14,FNetwork said they still face a budget
OL,15,Fshortfall of #1.1bn over the next two
OL,16,Fyears.
